Introduction

Kang So-eun (강소은), better known by her stage name Rina (리나), is the Lead Vocalist and Rapper of the girl group Weki Meki under Fantagio Music.

She debuted as a member of Weki Meki on August 8, 2017 with their first mini album "WEME".
